From the beginning of the Nova, everything are coming from ashes. Not so long time after the Falling corruption, the One began to spread out to the universe, creating a new government, they ruled every species in the universe upon their life and death. 
Disrespect the truth, the Lion clan rises as the force from the North Stars, coming from the Magna planets, they advands to the centre and claim their right, they called them the Rebellation.
